  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Toast almonds and walnuts in a skillet until golden brown.",
    "Mix together ground almonds, oatmeal, toasted nuts, honey, granulated sugar, milk, vanilla extract, and ground cumin. Add salt and optional truffle oil if using.",
    "Place mixture on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper and bake for 15 minutes.",
    "Reduce heat to 325°F (160°C) and continue baking until the crumble is golden brown and crisp, about 10 more minutes.",
    "Serve warm as dessert."
